A Fulani herdsman has been caught redhanded while transporting guns and AK47 bullets hidden in a bag of garri to Imo state. According to the Fulani herdsman, the cows he was moving were for a Fulani man while the guns and bullets are for his boss in Imo state. Watch the video of his confession below: Youths apprehend Fulani herdsman who was on his way to deliver guns and AK47 bullets, concealed inside a bag of garri to his boss in Imo state. pic.twitter.com/C5hyS31fzE Source